      • createSelectPopup

        public static void createSelectPopup​(java.lang.String path,
                                     java.lang.String title)
        This method creates a select popup window using an FXML file specified by the given path and sets the title of the window to the given title. The method also sets the window's resizability to false and makes the current screen unresponsive until the popup is closed.
        Parameters:
        path - the path to the FXML file to use for the popup window
        title - the title to be set for the popup window
